info.title: XigniteGlobalIndicesRealTime
info.description: This web service provides global real time information for U.S. and international indices.

GetRealTimeIndicesValueOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetRealTimeIndicesValueResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetRealTimeIndicesValueResult>
    <tns:IndexValue><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
     <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
     <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
     <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
     <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
     <tns:Index>
      <tns:IndexName>string</tns:IndexName>
      <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
      <tns:IndexGroup>string</tns:IndexGroup>
      <tns:Valoren><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Valoren>
      <tns:Currency>string</tns:Currency>
     </tns:Index>
     <tns:Value>
      <tns:Date>string</tns:Date>
      <tns:Time>string</tns:Time>
      <tns:UTCOffset><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:UTCOffset>
      <tns:Volume><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Volume>
      <tns:Open><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Open>
      <tns:High><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:High>
      <tns:Low><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Low>
      <tns:Last><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Last>
      <tns:Close><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Close>
      <tns:ChangeFromOpen><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ChangeFromOpen>
      <tns:PercentChangeFromOpen><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PercentChangeFromOpen>
      <tns:PreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PreviousClose>
      <tns:PreviousCloseDate>string</tns:PreviousCloseDate>
      <tns:ChangeFromPreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ChangeFromPreviousClose>
      <tns:PercentChangeFromPreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PercentChangeFromPreviousClose>
     </tns:Value>
    </tns:IndexValue>
   </tns:GetRealTimeIndicesValueResult>
  </tns:GetRealTimeIndicesValueResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
